\id COL NKO Paul's Letter to the Colossians in the Nkonya Language of Ghana
\h Kolosefɔ
\toc1 Ɔwʋlʋ́á Paulo Lɔ́wanlɩ́n Sɩ́sɩ́ Kolosefɔ
\toc2 Kolosefɔ
\toc3 Kol.
\mt2 Ɔwʋlʋ́á Paulo Lɔ́wanlɩ́n Sɩ́sɩ́
\mt1 Kolosefɔ
\c 1
\rem Proofread 07-07-09
\s1 Itsiáha
\p 
\v 1-2 Mɩ́ Paulo ánɩ́ Bulu apɛ́ sʋ nabwɛ́ Yesu Kristo sumbí ɔyɔpʋ́ pʋ́ anɩ píó Timoteo dɛ́ ɔwʋlʋ́ ánfɩ wanlɩ́n.
\p Anɩdɛ́pʋsɩ́sɩ́ anɩ apíóá bʋgyi Bulu ahá, bʋbʋ Kolose wúlutɔ, bʋbʋ ɔnɔkwalɩ há Kristo Yesu, mʋa amʋ́nyɔ ɛ́ babwɛ́ kʋlɛ.
\p Anɩ Sɩ́ Bulu mʋa anɩ Wíe Yesu Kristo bʋgyíi mlɩ bʋalɛ, abʋha mlɩ iwilwii.
\s1 Ɩpánda Mpáɩ
\p 
\v 3 Anɩtɛdá anɩ Wíe Yesu Kristo mʋ Sɩ Bulu ɩpán brégyíbrɛ́á anɩdɛ́ mpáɩ bɔ mlɩ nwunsʋ.
\v 4 Tsúfɛ́ anɩlanú ánɩ́ mlɩlɔ́hɔ Kristo Yesu gyi, mlɩbʋ ɔdwɛ ɛ́ há Bulu ahá fɛ́ɛ́.
\v 5 Mlɩdɛ́ ɔkpa kɩ́ɩ ha tɔ́á bapʋ́yáɩ́ há mlɩ ɔsʋ́sʋ́; fɛ́ alɩá mlɩyin tsú brɛ́á mlɩlégyankpá nu ɔnɔkwalɩ asʋ́n ámʋ́ʋ́ igyi Bulu asʋn wankláán ámʋ.
\v 6 \w Asʋn wankláán\w* ámʋ kɛ́n dɛ́klɛɩ́ wá ɔyɩ́tɔ́, ɩdɛ ahá tsiátɔ́ tsɛ́ɛ ɔtɩ́nɛgyíɔtɩ́nɛ́; fɛ́ alɩá ɩlɛtsɛ mlɩ tsú ɛkɛá mlɩlónu mʋ́, mlɩlɛ́bɩ ánɩ́ lɛ́lɛ́ Bulu tegyi ahá bʋalɛ.
\v 7 Anɩ osúmba ɔdwɛpʋ́ Epafra gyí ɔhá ánɩ́ ɔlɔpʋ asʋn wankláán ámʋ ba mlɩ. Yesu Kristo osúmbi ɔnɔkwalɩpʋ ogyi, ɔdɛ mlɩ bʋá anɩ ɔfansʋ.\f + \fr 1:7 \fqa Mlɩ ɔfansʋ \ft bʋ nwʋlʋ́ dada amʋ akʋtɔ.\f*
\v 8 Mʋlɛ́bá bɛbláa anɩ ɔdwɛá \w Ɔŋɛ Wankɩ́hɛ́\w* amʋ lapʋ́wá mlɩtɔ.
\p 
\v 9 Mʋ́ sʋ anɩmɔ́kʋ́sí mpáɩ bɔ mlɩ nwunsʋ tsú ɛkɛá anɩlónu mlɩ ɩwɩ asʋ́n ánfɩ. Anɩdɛ́ Bulu kokóli anɩaa, ɔháa amlɩbɩ mʋ apɛ́ kugyíkʋ wankláán. Ɔháa mʋ Ɔŋɛ Wankɩ́hɛ́ amʋ ɔha mlɩ nyánsa mʋ́a asʋ́n asɩnu fɛ́ɛ́,
\v 10 mɛ́nɩ mlɛ́talɩ́ tsíá tsiátɔ́á ɩbɔ́wa anɩ Wíe numnyam, amlɩgyi mʋ ansɩ́ ɔkpagyíɔkpasʋ. Ɔháa amlɩbwɛ yilé brégyíbrɛ́, trá bɩ Bulu tsɩa.
\v 11-12 Anɩa ɔháa mʋ túmiá mʋ́ ɔnɔ́ bʋ ɔnlɩn ɩwa mlɩ ɔwʋnlɩ́n, amlɩtalɩ tomi, nya klʋn, pʋ ansigyí da anɩ Sɩ́ Bulu ɩpán. Mʋláhá mlɩlafʋn ánɩ́ mlɩa mʋ ahá mlénya agyapadɩɛ ámʋ́ʋ́ alalá yáɩ́ mʋ iwíegyí wankɩ́hɛ́tɔ ámʋ ɩkʋ.
\v 13 Tsúfɛ́ mʋlálɛ́ anɩ tsú ɔhá ámʋ́ʋ́ ɔdɛ oklúnsʋ gyí amʋ túmi asɩ, pʋ́ anɩ ba mʋ Bi ɔdwɛpʋ́ ámʋ iwíegyí amʋtɔ.
\v 14 Mʋ Bi ánfɩsʋ ɔlɔtsʋn hɔ anɩ, alasí anɩ lakpan kíé anɩ nɩ́.
\s1 Kristo Dʋn Tógyítɔ́
\p 
\v 15 Ɔhaa tamawun Bulu, Kristotɔ ɔlɛlɩn ɔwan. Ɔbʋ ɩnʋ asa Bulu lɔ́bwɛ tógyítɔ́, ɔdʋn Bulu ɩtɔ bwɛhɛ́ kugyíkʋ.
\v 16 Mʋsʋ́ Bulu lɔ́tsʋn bwɛ tógyítɔ́á ɩbʋ ɔsʋ́ mʋ́a asɩ. Mʋ́á bʋtowun pʋ́ mʋ́á bʋtamawun fɛ́ɛ́, ɔŋɛ́tɔ́ awíe, ɔmásʋ́gyí túmi, atúmipʋ, pʋ́ ɩsʋ agyípʋ́ fɛ́ɛ́. Mʋsʋ́ Bulu lɔ́tsʋn bwɛ ɔyɩ́ fɛ́ɛ́, pʋ́wá mʋ numnyam.
\v 17 Ɔbʋ ɩnʋ asa tógyítɔ́ lefi asɩ. Mʋsʋ́ atɔ́ ámʋ fɛ́ɛ́ ɩdɛ agyʋ́má yɔ wá abatɔ.
\v 18 Mʋgyí nwun há mʋ nyankpʋsa-oyí, igyi ɔpasua ámʋ, ɔdɛ mʋ́ nkpa ha. Mʋlégyankpá kʋsʋ́ tsú afúlitɔ, ogyi tógyítɔ́ nkpá ogyápʋ.
\v 19 Tsúfɛ́ ɩbʋ Bulu ɔdwɛ ánɩ́ mʋ tsiátɔ́ fɛ́ɛ́ bétsiá mʋ Bi ámʋtɔ.
\v 20 Mʋsʋ́ Bulu lɔ́tsʋn yinkía tógyítɔ́ ba mʋ ɩwɩ wá. Ɔlɔtsʋn mʋ obugya amʋ́ʋ́ ɩlɔwʋlɩ́ asɩ brɛ́á bɛda mʋ mántá \w oyikpalíhɛ\w* amʋsʋ pʋ́ iwilwii wá mʋa tógyítɔ́ nsɩnɛ́. Mʋ́a ɩbʋ ɔsʋ́sʋ́ pʋ́ mʋ́á ɩbʋ ɔsʋlʋ́sʋ fɛ́ɛ́.
\p 
\v 21 Tɛkɩ mlɩ ɛ́ mlɩlɛ́damlí ɔma há Bulu, mlɩgyí mʋ alupʋ́ mlɩ asʋ́n susúhɛ pʋ́ mlɩ bwɛhɛ́ laláhɛ sʋ.
\v 22 Támɛ séi á, ɩtráa megyí alɩ. Kristo lɔ́bwɛ nyankpʋsa, olowu. Bulu lɔ́tsʋn mʋ oyikpalíhɛsʋ lowu ámʋsʋ lá mlɩa mʋnyɔ nsɩnɛ́. Mʋ́ sʋ ifin pʋ́ asʋansʋ má mlɩ ɩwɩ, ɔbɛ́kpa mlɩ ba mʋ ansɩ́tɔ́.
\v 23 Támɛ ilehián ánɩ́ mlɔ́hɔ asʋ́nsʋ́ ánfɩ gyi, lɩ́ɩ́ kínkíínkín. Mlɩmáha abʋtsɛ mlɩ agywɩɩn lɛ ɩtɔ́ ámʋ́ʋ́ mlɩdɛ́ mʋ́ ɔkpa kɩ́ɩ, asʋn wankláán ámʋ lapʋ́ba mlɩ ámʋsʋ. Asʋn wankláán ánfɩ osúmpʋ́ mɩ́ Paulo ngyi nɩ́. Asʋ́n ánfɩ ɔkan bʋdɛda ɔyɩ́tɔ́ fɛ́ɛ́ ɛ́ nɩ́.
\p 
\v 24 Ɩbʋ mɩ ansigyí ánɩ́ ndɛ ipian wúun mlɩ sʋ. Tsúfɛ́ ndɛ ɩwɩɔsɩn ámʋ́ʋ́ Kristo lówun sian amʋ kʋ wúun ha mʋ ɔpasua, igyi mʋ nyankpʋsa-oyí ámʋ.
\v 25 Bulu lɔ́pʋ mʋ asʋ́n wankláán ámʋ wá mɩ́ ɩbɩtɔ, ánɩ́ ndáa mʋ́ fɛ́ɛ́ ɔkan suna mlɩ, ampʋsum ɔpasua ámʋ.
\v 26 Ɔlɔpʋ asʋ́n ánfɩ ŋáín bɩ́mbɩ́ ɔpá, támɛ alalɛ́ mʋ́ ɔwan súná mʋ ahá séi.
\v 27 Ɩbʋ Bulu ɔdwɛ ánɩ́ ɔbɛ́lɛ mʋ́ ɔwan súná mlɩá mlɩmégyí Yudafɔ. Asʋn ŋaínhɛ́ amʋ gyí, Kristo tsie mlɩtɔ. Ɩbʋ ibíá, ɩbʋ numnyam ɛ́. Mʋ́désuná ánɩ́ abénya mʋ numnyam amʋ ɩkʋ nɩ́.
\v 28 Mʋ ɩwɩ asʋ́n anɩdɛ́ ahá fɛ́ɛ́ bláa, anɩdɛ́ amʋ́ ɔlá da, pʋ́ nyánsa ámʋ́ʋ́ Bulu lahá anɩ ámʋ súná amʋ́ atɔ́; mɛ́nɩ bɔ́fʋn, abɛ́kpa amʋ́ ba Bulu, amʋ́a Kristo ɩkʋlɛbwɛtɔ́.
\v 29 Ɩ́nɩ sʋ nahɩ́ɛ́ ndɛprɩ́ɩ, pʋ Kristo túmi ámʋ́ʋ́ ɩbʋ mɩtɔ ámʋ yɔ́ agyʋ́má nɩ́.
\c 2
\rem Proofread 07-07-09
\p 
\v 1 Ndekléá mlɩbɩ́ɩ ɩprɩ́ɩ ánɩ́ ndɛprɩ́ɩ ɔwʋnlɩ́nsʋ́, mlɩa ɔpasua ámʋ́ʋ́ ɩbʋ Laodikea pʋ́ ahá ámʋ́ʋ́ bʋmɔkʋ́wun mɩ kɩ amʋ fɛ́ɛ́ nwunsʋ.
\v 2 Ndɛ mʋ́ bwɛ pʋ́wá amʋ́ ɔwʋnlɩ́n, abʋbwɛ kʋlɛ, dwɛ aba, nu asʋ́n asɩ wankláán, mɛ́nɩ bónu Bulu asʋ́n ŋaínhɛ́ amʋ́ʋ́ igyi Kristo amʋ fɛ́ɛ́ asɩ.
\v 3 Kristotɔ Bulu lɔ́pʋ mʋ atonyahɛ́á igyi mʋ nyánsa pʋ́ mʋ asʋ́nbɩ fɛ́ɛ́ wá.
\p 
\v 4 Ndɛ mlɩ asʋ́n ánfɩ bláa, mɛ́nɩ ɔhaa mɔ́ɔpʋ asʋ́n ánɩ́ ɩbʋ anulɛ́ kʋkʋ bɛmlɛ́ mlɩ.
\v 5 Ɩbʋ mʋ́tɔ́á mbʋ ɩfɔ́ mlɩ wá, támɛ ntosúsu mlɩ ɩwɩ brégyíbrɛ́. Ansɩ́ ɛ́ ɩdɛ mɩ́ gyí ánɩ́ mlɩtsie wankláán, mlɩlɩ́ɩ́ kínkíínkín Kristosʋ hógyitɔ.
\v 6 Ɩ́nɩá mlɩlahɔ Kristo Yesu gyi ánɩ́ mʋgyí mlɩ Wíe sʋ á, mlɩyɔ mʋ́sʋ́ mlɩa mʋnyɔ amlɩbwɛ kʋlɛ.
\v 7 Mlɩ ɛ́ mlɩhɩɛ lɩɩ kínkíínkín Kristo hógyitɔ, amlɩnya ɔwʋnlɩ́n tsu mlɩa mʋnyɔ ɩkʋlɛbwɛtɔ. Mlɩyɔ mʋ́sʋ́ amlɩhɔ mʋ ɩwɩ asʋ́n ámʋ́ʋ́ bʋdɛ mlɩ suná, igyi ɔnɔkwalɩ amʋ, fɛ́ alɩá oyí nlín tɔyɔ́ ɔtɔ́tɔ́ɔ́tɔ́, yódúnká ntsu há mʋ́ ɩtɛdan, amlɩda Bulu ɩpán ɛ́ brégyíbrɛ́.
\p 
\v 8 Mlɩmáha ɔkpa ɔhaa ɔmlɛ mlɩ, pʋ mʋ ansɩtɩ́ɩn mʋ́a afunu asʋ́n ánɩ́ igyi amándɩ́ɛ́á anyánkpʋ́sa bɔwa kʋkʋ, itsú ɔŋɛ́ ntɛ́ɛ túmiá ɩdɛ ɔyɩ́ ánfɩsʋ gyí, imotsú Kristo wá bɛha amlɩmli mʋ nkpábi.
\v 9 Tsúfɛ́ Kristotɔ Bulu tsiátɔ́ onutónutó ámʋ fɛ́ɛ́ ɩbʋ nyankpʋsa ɔkpasʋ.
\v 10 Ɩ́nɩá mlɩa Kristonyɔ mlɩlabwɛ́ kʋlɛ sʋ mlɩlafʋn. Mʋgyí ɔhá ánɩ́ ɔbʋ túmi ɔŋɛ́tɔ́ atúmipʋ pʋ́ ɩsʋ agyípʋ́ fɛ́ɛ́sʋ́.
\p 
\v 11 Mlɩa mʋnyɔ ɩkʋlɛbwɛ sʋ aladɩ́nkɩ́ mlɩ tsiátɔ́ dada amʋ lɛ́ mlɩsʋ fɛ́ alɩ ámʋ́ʋ́ bʋtɛtɩn \w keté\w*, dɩ́nkɩ́ awʋlɩ lɛ́ mʋ́sʋ́ ámʋ.
\v 12 Brɛ́á bɔbɔ mlɩ asú á, bopulá mlɩ tsiátɔ́ dada amʋ fɛ́ alɩá bopulá Kristo; Bulu lɔ́kʋsʋ́a mlɩ ba nkpatɔ fɛ́ alɩá ɔlɔkʋsʋ́a Kristo, tsúfɛ́ mlɩlóhogyi ánɩ́ Bulu bʋ túmi kʋ́sʋ́a mʋ tsú afúlitɔ.
\v 13 Tɛkɩ mlɩ lakpan pʋ́ mlɩ tsiátɔ́ dada amʋ́ʋ́ bʋmɔkʋ́dɩ́nkɩ́ lɛ́ mlɩsʋ ámʋ sʋ mlɩlówu fɛ́ ɔhá ánɩ́ ɔmɔkʋ́tɩn keté. Támɛ séi á, Bulu lakʋ́sʋ́a anɩa Kristonyɔ ba nkpa pɔpwɛtɔ, alasí anɩ lakpan fɛ́ɛ́ kíé anɩ.
\v 14 Ɔlɛdɩnkɩ́ asʋ́n ámʋ́ʋ́ bɔwanlɩ́n wá Mose mblatɔ, ɩdɛ anɩ ɩlá lɛ ámʋ lɛ́ anɩsʋ, yɛ́da mʋ́ mántá Kristo \w oyikpalíhɛ\w* amʋsʋ.
\v 15 Bulu lɔ́swɩɩ́ ɔŋɛ́tɔ́ atúmipʋ pʋ́ ɩsʋ agyípʋ́ túmi, ɔlɛkɩtá amʋ́ ndoun, lɛ́ amʋ́ ɔwan, wá amʋ́ pɛ́lɩtɔ, brɛ́ olegyi amʋ́sʋ́ Kristo oyikpalíhɛ amʋsʋ.
\p 
\v 16 Mʋ́ sʋ mlɩmáha ɔhaa ɔlɛ mlɩ ɩlá mlɩ atogyihɛ, mlɩ atonuhɛ, nkegyí, ɔtsra pɔpwɛ nkɛ, ntɛ́ɛ Yudafɔ \w ɔkpʋ́nʋ́ ɔdakɛ́\w* aná sʋ.
\v 17 Yiyí kɛkɛ ɩ́nɩ fɛ́ɛ́ igyi há atɔ́ ámʋ́ʋ́ ɩbɛ́ba amʋ onutó. Mʋ́ onutónutó ámʋ lɛ́lɩn ɔwan Kristotɔ.
\v 18 Mlɩmáha ɔkpa ɔhaa ɔmlɛ mlɩ amlɩba ɩwɩasɩ sum Bulu-abɔpʋ, amlɩhʋlɩ ɩpán ánɩ́ Bulu lɛ́hɩɛ yáɩ́ mlɩ. Nɩ́ ɔbɛ́ɛ alawun tɔkʋ tsú mʋ́ ɩwɩ kʋ́ráá pó á, ɔyɩ́tɔ́ ansɩtɩ́ɩn láhá mʋ ɔdɛ ɩwɩ tsu.
\v 19 Ɔhá ánfɩ odu lamáɩ́n ɩwɩ lɛ́ Kristo amʋ́ʋ́ ógyi ɔpasua ámʋ nwun ámʋsʋ. Tsúfɛ́ ɔpasua ámʋtɔ anɩ fɛ́ɛ́ anɩlɛ́tsa abasʋ, Kristo amʋ́ʋ́ ogyi nwun ámʋ dɛ́ anɩ ɔwʋnlɩ́n wa, mɛ́nɩ abɛ́dan alɩá Bulu déklé.
\p 
\v 20 Mlɩa Kristonyɔ lówu. Mʋ́ sʋ mlɩtráa mlɩmá ɔyɩ́tɔ́ túmi kʋkʋ asɩ. Ntogyi sʋ́ mlɩtráa mlɩdɛ́ mbla ánfɩ anásʋ́ gyí?
\v 21 Bɛɛ, “Mágyi ɩ́nɩ. Mápʋ ɩbɩ da ɩ́nɩ, mátsu ɩ́nɩ ɛ́!”
\v 22 Nɩ́ bɔpʋ́ ntobí ánfɩ fɛ́ɛ́ bwɛ́ atɔ́ tá á, iteyíntá. Anyánkpʋ́sa onutó mbla pʋ́ amʋ́ atosunáhɛ́ igyi.
\v 23 Anɩdɛ́ mbla ánfɩ kɩ́ɩ fɛ́ tɔ́á nyánsa bʋ mʋ́tɔ́, ɩbɛ́ha abɔ́wa alɛ́ Bulu ansɩ́tɔ́, abɛ́ba ɩwɩasɩ há mʋ, wá ɩwɩ ɔsɩn anɩaa ɩbɛ́ha abɛ́bɩ gyi ɩwɩsʋ. Támɛ ɩ́nɩ aná fɛ́ɛ́ ɩmɛ́ɛtalɩ́ há anɩméegyi ɩwɩsʋ.
\c 3
\rem Proofread 07-07-09
\s1 Nkpa Pɔpwɛ Tsiá
\p 
\v 1 Mʋ́ sʋ nɩ́ Bulu lakʋ́sʋ́a mlɩa Kristonyɔ ba nkpa pɔpwɛtɔ á, mlɩdunka atɔ́á ɩbʋ ɔsʋ́sʋ́, ɔtɩ́nɛ́ ámʋ́ʋ́ Kristo tsie Bulu gyɔpɩsʋ ámʋ.
\v 2 Mlɩha agywɩɩn ɩnʋ atɔ́ ɩwɩ, megyí ɔsʋlʋ́sʋ klɛ́.
\v 3 Tsúfɛ́ mlɩlawú, Bulu lapʋ́ mlɩa Kristonyɔ nkpa onutó ŋáín mʋtɔ.
\v 4 Ɛkɛá ɔbɛ́lɛ Kristo amʋ́ʋ́ ogyi mlɩ nkpa onutó ámʋ ɔwan súná ɔyɩ́ á, ɛkɛ ámʋ kɛ́n ɔbɛ́lɛ mlɩa mʋnyɔ ɔwan mʋ numnyamtɔ nɩ́.
\s1 Tsiátɔ́ Dada Mʋ́a Pɔ́pwɛ
\p 
\v 5 Mʋ́ sʋ mlɩmɔ tsiátɔ́ dada amʋ́ʋ́ ɩbʋ mlɩtɔ ámʋ. Mʋ́gyí; atsɩ mʋ́a ayin asʋ́nwa, ifintotsiá, ɔwɔ́lɩ laláhɛ mʋ́a pɛ́lɩla. Ɔyɩ́ ánfɩtɔ atɔ wankláán ɩmápɛ mlɩ ansɩ́, tsúfɛ́ ɔnsɩ́pɛ igyi fɛ́ ɔkpɩsúm.
\v 6 Ntobí ánfɩ odu abwɛpʋ́sʋ́ Bulu tɛhɩ́ɛ́ nyá ɔblɔ́ nɩ́.
\v 7 Mʋ́ aná mlɩtɔbwɛ́ brɛ́á mlɩgyí ɔmátɔ́fɔ nɩ́.
\p 
\v 8 Séi gyí brɛ́á mlɛ́lɛ ɔblɔ́, ɔblɔ́kpán, olu, abakpɔɩ́, asʋkpan blɩ́ aná lɛ́ mlɩtɔ nɩ́.
\v 9 Mlɩmáwa afunu súná aba, tsúfɛ́ mlɩlasí mlɩ tsiátɔ́ dada amʋ pʋ́ mʋ́ bwɛhɛ́ fɛ́ɛ́.
\v 10 Mlɩlalátsú tsiátɔ́ pɔpwɛ. Bulu gyí mʋ́ Ɔbwɛpʋ́, ɔdɛ mʋ́ bwɛ pɔ́pwɛ lɩan mʋ ɩwɩ brɛ́ ánfɩ mlɩdɛ́ mʋ bɩ ánfɩ.
\v 11 Tsiátɔ́ pɔpwɛ anfɩ mʋ́ á, ɩmɛfáhʋn ánɩ́ Griikiyin ntɛ́ɛ Yudayin fʋgyi. Fɛtɩn \w keté\w* ntɛ́ɛ fʋmɛtɩn, ɔkpʋtɔ́pʋ ntɛ́ɛ okudasɩ́yin, ɔkpábi ntɛ́ɛ ɔdɩ́hɩɛ fʋ́gyi. Kristo gyí tógyítɔ́, ɔbʋ amʋ́ fɛ́ɛ́tɔ́.
\p 
\v 12 Mʋ́ sʋ ɩ́nɩá Bulu lalɛ́ mlɩ pʋ́bwɛ́ mʋ ahá ánɩ́ amʋ́ ɩwɩ latɩn pʋ́ mʋ adwɛpʋ́ á, mlɩha nwewúun, awɩtɔlɛwa, ɩwɩasɩbá, ilwií pʋ́ klʋnya itsia mlɩtɔ.
\v 13 Mlɩnya ɩklʋn ha aba. Nɩ́ ɔkʋ mʋa mʋ ba benya á, mlɩsikie aba fɛ́ alɩá Kristo lési mlɩ klɛ́ kíé mlɩ.
\v 14 Mʋ́á ɩdʋn a, ɔdwɛ tɔ́bwɛ́ anɩ fɛ́ɛ́ ɩkʋlɛ. Ɩbwɛ́ɛ mlɩ tati dɩdáhɛ́.
\v 15 Mlɩha Kristo iwilwii igyí mlɩ klʋnsʋ, tsúfɛ́ mʋ́tɔ́ Bulu latɩ́ mlɩ bɔwa; mlɩa mʋ nyankpʋsa-oyí ámʋ mlɩlabwɛ́ kʋlɛ nɩ. Mlɩda mʋ ɩpán ɛ́ brégyíbrɛ́.
\v 16 Mlɩha Kristo asʋ́n ámʋ ɩhɩɛ bʋla mlɩ klʋntɔ, ɩha mlɩ nyánsa. Mlɩpʋtɔɩ kpla aba, suna aba atɔ́. Mlɩwa \w Israelfɔ ɩlʋ\w*, ɔsankuosʋ ɩlʋ pʋ́ ɔŋɛ́tɔ́ ɩlʋ mlɩ klʋntɔ pʋtsu Bulu fʋa, pʋda anɩ Sɩ́ Bulu ɩpán.
\v 17 Mlɩ atɔ bwɛhɛ́ pʋ́ mlɩ asʋn blɩ́hɛ́ fɛ́ɛ́ ɩbwɛ́ɛ anɩ Wíe Yesu ɩdátɔ́, amlɩpʋ ɩpán ha anɩ Sɩ́ Bulu tsʋn mʋsʋ.
\s1 Akristofɔ Tsiátɔ́
\p 
\v 18 Aká, mlɩba ɩwɩasɩ ha mlɩ akúlu alɩá ɩlɛkanáa ha ahá ánɩ́ bʋgyi Kristo klɛ́.
\p 
\v 19 Akúlu, mlɩ ɛ́ mlɩdwɛ mlɩ aká. Mlɩmábwɛ amʋ́ kpóunkpóun.
\p 
\v 20 Abí, mlɩbu mlɩ akwɩɩ́pʋ́, tsúfɛ́ mʋ́ Bulu tekle nɩ.
\p 
\v 21 Akwɩɩ́pʋ́, mlɩmáwa mlɩ abí ɔblɔ́, mɛ́nɩ ɩwɩ móowu amʋ́.
\p 
\v 22 Nkpábi, mlɩbu mlɩ ɔsʋlʋ́sʋ awíe tógyítɔ́á mlɔ́bwɛtɔ. Mlɩha amʋ́ ansɩ́ igyi mlɩ ɩwɩ brégyíbrɛ́, megyí amʋ́ ansɩ́tɔ́ wʋlɛ. Mlɩbwɛ mʋ́ tsú klʋntɔ, tsúfɛ́ mlɩtobú anɩ Wíe.
\v 23 Mlɩbwɛ tógyítɔ́ tsu mlɩ klʋntɔ, fɛ́ anɩ Wíe mlɩdɛ́ mʋ́ bwɛ há, megyí anyánkpʋ́sa.
\v 24 Mlɩkaɩn ánɩ́ anɩ Wíe ɩbɩtɔ mlénya mlɩ ɩkɔká ánɩ́ alalá yáɩ́ mʋ abí. Tsúfɛ́ Kristo gyí Owíe ánɩ́ mlɩdésum.
\v 25 Támɛ nɩ́ fɔbwɛ́ tɔ́á ɩma alɛ a, ɔbɛ́ka fʋ́ ɩkɔ, tsúfɛ́ ɔtamakɩ ɔhaa ansɩ́tɔ́.
\c 4
\rem Proofread 07-07-09
\p 
\v 1 Nkpábi awíe, mlɩpʋ tɔ́á ɩbʋ alɛ́, igyi ɔnɔkwalɩ kpa mlɩ nkpábi, tsúfɛ́ mlɩ ɛ́ mlɩbʋ Owíe ɔsʋ́sʋ́.
\p 
\v 2 Mlɩkɩta mpaɩbɔ́tɔ́. Mlɩdɩnka ansɩ́ ɩwɩsʋ, ɩpánda ɛ́ itsia mlɩ klʋntɔ.
\v 3 Mlɩbɔ mpáɩ ha anɩ ɛ́. Bulu ofínki ɔkpa ha anɩ atalɩ da Kristo ɩwɩ asʋn ŋaínhɛ́ amʋ ɔkan. Mʋ́ sʋ nda obu nɩ́.
\v 4 Mlɩbɔ mpáɩ mlɩaa, ndáa mʋ́ ɔkan wankláán, alɩá ilehián.
\p 
\v 5 Mlɩkɩ mlɩ nátɩtɔ ɔmátɔ́fɔtɔ. Nɩ́ ɔkpa ifínkí há mlɩ á, mlɩmáyintá mʋ́.
\v 6 Mlɩ ɩtɔ́ɩ ɩwa anulɛ́, ɩwa labi, mɛ́nɩ mlɛ́talɩ́ lɛ́ ɔhagyíɔha asʋn fɩtɛ́hɛ́ ɔnɔ́ wankláán.
\s1 Ɩklá
\p 
\v 7 Anɩa opíó ɔdwɛpʋ́ Tihiko dɛ́ anɩ Wíe agyʋ́má yɔ. Osúmpʋ́ ɔnɔkwalɩpʋ ogyi. Ɔbɛ́bláa mlɩ alɩá mɩ́ ɩwɩ gyí fɛ́ɛ́.
\v 8 Nawá mʋ mlɩ wá mbɛ́ɛ, ɔbɛ́bláa mlɩ alɩá anɩ ɩwɩ gyí, ɔwa mlɩ atɛtɔ-ɔnlɩn.
\v 9 Mʋa anɩ píó ɔdwɛpʋ́ ɔnɔkwalɩpʋ Onesimo, ogyi mlɩ pɩ amʋ ɔbɛ́ba bɛbla mlɩ asʋ́n ánɩ́ ɩlaba nfɩ fɛ́ɛ́.
\p 
\v 10 Aristarko, mɩ́ bá ánɩ́ mɩ́a mʋnyɔ anɩda obu ɔhá mlɩ itsiá. Alɩ kɛ́n Marko, ogyi Barnaba mʋ pio ámʋ ɛ́ ɔhá mlɩ itsiá nɩ́. Mlɩhɔ Marko ɔfɔɔ́ wankláán, nɩ́ ɔlɔtsʋn ba mlɩ wá fɛ́ alɩá nɛbláa mlɩ yáɩ́.
\v 11 Opíó Yesu, bʋtɛtráa tɩ mʋ Yusto ɛ́ ɔhá mlɩ itsiá. Ahá abasá ánfɩ pɛ́ gyí Yudafɔá mɩ́a amʋ́nyɔ anɩdɛ́ \w Bulu iwíegyí\w* ámʋ ɩwɩ agyʋ́má yɔ nɩ́. Amʋ́ tɛ́kɩ́tá klʋn wá mɩ́ ɩwɩtɔ nɩ́.
\p 
\v 12 Epafra, otsú mlɩ wá, ogyi Kristo Yesu osúmbi amʋ ɛ́ ɔhá mlɩ itsiá. Ɔtɛhɩ́ɛ́ bɔ mpáɩ há mlɩ ánɩ́ Bulu ɔwáa mlɩ ɔwʋnlɩ́n, ɔha amlɩfʋn, amlɩtalɩ bwɛ Bulu apɛ́ kugyíkʋ.
\v 13 Nɛ́talɩ́ gyí mʋ ɩwɩ adánsɩɛ ánɩ́ ɔhɩ́ɛ́ ɔdɛ agyʋ́má yɔ mlɩa Akristofɔá bʋbʋ Laodikea pʋ́ Hierapoli ɩdátɔ́.
\v 14 Anɩ ɔdwɛpʋ́ Luka, ogyi ɩlɔ ɔtsapʋ́ mʋa Dema bɛhá mlɩ itsiá.
\p 
\v 15 Nɛhá anɩ apíó Laodikeafɔ ámʋ itsiá. Nɛhá Nunfa mʋa ɔpasua ámʋ́ʋ́ ɩbʋ mʋ wóyítɔ́ amʋ ɛ́ itsiá.
\v 16 Nɩ́ mlɛkla ɔwʋlʋ́ ánfɩ súná ɔpasua ámʋ tá á, mlɩpʋsɩsɩ Laodikeafɔ ɛ́. Mlɩkla amʋ́ klɛ́ ámʋ́ʋ́ nɔpʋsɩ́sɩ́ amʋ́ ámʋ ɛ́.
\v 17 Mlɩbla Arkipo mlɩaa, ɔmɔ́ɔ agyʋ́má ámʋ́ʋ́ Bulu lɔ́pʋwá mʋ ɩbɩtɔ ámʋ ɔnɔ́ wankláán.
\p 
\v 18 Mɩ́ Paulo, onutónutó lawá ɩbɩ ɔwʋlʋ́ ánfɩ asɩ. Mlɩmátan ánɩ́ nda obu.
\p Bulu ogyíi mlɩ bʋalɛ.
